An ear training application
======

To see a live version, visit http://polarbear1337.herokuapp.com/
A test account is pre-populated: user:test@test.com pass:1234

To run locally, follow the steps below:

Requirements
------
* Node.js
* MongoDB

Usage
------
Install Dependencies:

```
$ npm install
```

Start mongodb:

```
$ mongod
```

Start the Server:

```
$ node app.js
```

Open browser and nagivate to

```
localhost:3000
```

